# Routes

- Always namespace under :api, :v1
- Use `defaults: { format: :json }` on the namespace
- Use `only:` to whitelist actions — never use `except:`
- Member routes for custom actions (calculate, compare, report)
- Health check outside the namespace: `get '/api/health', to: 'health#show'`
- Example structure:
  namespace :api do
    namespace :v1 do
      resources :farms, only: [:index, :create, :show, :update, :destroy] do
        resources :fields, only: [:index, :create, :show, :update, :destroy]
      end
    end
  end